{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"C++基础结构","date":"2022-05-01T15:15:58.000Z","updated":"2024-05-16T18:15:29.693Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C++基础结构.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"组成\"><a href=\"#组成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组成\"></a>组成</h1><p>一个基本的C++程序通常包含以下几个部分：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>预处理器指令</strong>：预处理器指令以 <code>#</code> 符号开头，它们告诉编译器在编译之前进行某些操作。例如，<code>#include</code> 用于包含头文件。</li>\n<li><strong>主函数</strong>：C++程序从 <code>main()</code> 函数开始执行。<code>main</code> 函数是C++程序的入口点。</li>\n<li><strong>声明和定义</strong>：在 <code>main()</code> 函数之前，可以声明变量和函数，并定义类、结构体等。</li>\n<li><strong>执行语句</strong>：在 <code>main()</code> 函数中，可以编写执行语句来执行程序。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>下面是一个简单的C++程序示例，它打印出 “Hello, World!”：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello, World!&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这个程序的各部分说明：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>#include &lt;iostream&gt;</code> 是预处理器指令，用于包含标准输入输出头文件。</li>\n<li><code>int main()</code> 是主函数，C++程序从这里开始执行。</li>\n<li><code>std::cout &lt;&lt; &quot;Hello, World!&quot;;</code> 是执行语句，它打印出 “Hello, World!”。</li>\n<li><code>return 0;</code> 表示程序正常结束。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"C-基础语句\"><a href=\"#C-基础语句\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"C++基础语句\"></a>C++基础语句</h1><p>范例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//备注</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"keyword\">include</span><span class=\"string\">&lt;iostream&gt;</span><span class=\"comment\">//头文件</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> std;<span class=\"comment\">//命名空间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span><span class=\"comment\">//主函数入口</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"type\">int</span> value = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;<span class=\"comment\">//初始化整形变量</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcout &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&quot;The variable is initialized as :&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; value &lt;&lt; endl;<span class=\"comment\">//输出</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcout &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&quot;give a new value to this variable please.&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<span class=\"comment\">//输出</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcin &gt;&gt; value;<span class=\"comment\">//输入</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcout &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&quot;The variable changed to  :&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; value &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;<span class=\"comment\">//返回值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>声明语句：定义函数中使用的变量的名称和类型；</li>\n<li>赋值语句：使用赋值运算符对变量进行赋值；</li>\n<li>消息语句：将消息发送给对象，激发某种行动；</li>\n<li>函数调用：执行函数。被调用的函数执行完毕之后，程序返回到函数调用语句后面的语句；</li>\n<li>函数原型：声明函数的返回类型、函数接受的参数数量和类型；</li>\n<li>返回语句：将一个值从被调用的函数哪里返回到调用函数中。</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"函数\"><a href=\"#函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数\"></a>函数</h1><ol>\n<li>函数格式：<ul>\n<li>函数头和函数体</li>\n<li><code>type functionname(argumentlist)&#123; statements&#125;</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>函数特性：<ul>\n<li>函数头：指出返回值（如果有的话）的类型和函数期望通过参数传递给他的信息的类型。</li>\n<li>函数体：由一系列位于花括号中的C++语句组成；</li>\n<li>接受一个参数</li>\n<li>返回一个值</li>\n<li>需要一个原型</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>在多函数的程序中旨在需要使用到io指令的函数中使用using编译指令，只让需要访问std名称空间的函数访问更佳。</li>\n</ol>\n","feature":true,"text":"C++基础结构....","permalink":"/post/C++基础结构","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">组成</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#C-%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">C++基础语句</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">函数</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"kiyose408","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/c99588b4a60c4d698d7a66a0b1ea1567.jpeg","link":"/","description":"强风吹拂~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"C++的输入和输出","date":"2022-05-01T18:15:58.000Z","updated":"2024-05-16T18:17:36.240Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C++的输入和输出.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"C++的输入和输出....","permalink":"/post/C++的输入和输出","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"8.4k","symbolsTime":"8 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"kiyose408","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/c99588b4a60c4d698d7a66a0b1ea1567.jpeg","link":"/","description":"强风吹拂~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{}}